@startuml
!theme plain

title Waze CCP Processor - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor "Waze CCP API" as WazeAPI
participant "CloudWatch Events" as CloudWatch
participant "waze-data-download\nLambda" as DownloadLambda
participant "S3 Bucket\n(Data Lake)" as S3
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "waze-data-process\nLambda" as ProcessLambda
participant "waze-data-alerts-processing\nLambda" as AlertsLambda
participant "waze-data-jams-processing\nLambda" as JamsLambda
participant "waze-data-irregularities-processing\nLambda" as IrregularitiesLambda
participant "Aurora PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as Database
participant "waze-db-initialize\nLambda" as DBInitLambda
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "waze-data-api\nLambda" as APILambda
actor "Client" as Client

== Database Initialization ==
DBInitLambda -> Database: Initialize schema
activate DBInitLambda
activate Database
Database --> DBInitLambda: Schema created
deactivate Database
deactivate DBInitLambda

== Data Ingestion Flow ==
CloudWatch -> DownloadLambda: Trigger periodic execution
activate DownloadLambda
DownloadLambda -> WazeAPI: Fetch Waze CCP data
activate WazeAPI
WazeAPI --> DownloadLambda: Return JSON data
deactivate WazeAPI
DownloadLambda -> S3: Store raw JSON file
activate S3
S3 --> DownloadLambda: Confirmation
DownloadLambda -> SNS: Publish data retrieval notification
activate SNS
SNS --> DownloadLambda: Notification sent
deactivate SNS
deactivate DownloadLambda

== Data Processing Flow ==
S3 -> ProcessLambda: Trigger S3 event (new file)
activate ProcessLambda
ProcessLambda -> S3: Read JSON file
S3 --> ProcessLambda: Return JSON data
ProcessLambda -> ProcessLambda: Parse and validate data
ProcessLambda -> SQS: Send alerts data to queue
activate SQS
SQS --> ProcessLambda: Queued
ProcessLambda -> SQS: Send jams data to queue
SQS --> ProcessLambda: Queued
ProcessLambda -> SQS: Send irregularities data to queue
SQS --> ProcessLambda: Queued
deactivate ProcessLambda

SQS -> AlertsLambda: Trigger with alerts data
activate AlertsLambda
AlertsLambda -> AlertsLambda: Transform to relational schema
AlertsLambda -> Database: Insert alerts data
activate Database
Database --> AlertsLambda: Insert confirmation
deactivate Database
AlertsLambda -> SNS: Publish processing status
activate SNS
SNS --> AlertsLambda: Notification sent
deactivate SNS
deactivate AlertsLambda

SQS -> JamsLambda: Trigger with jams data
activate JamsLambda
JamsLambda -> JamsLambda: Transform to relational schema
JamsLambda -> Database: Insert jams data
activate Database
Database --> JamsLambda: Insert confirmation
deactivate Database
JamsLambda -> SNS: Publish processing status
activate SNS
SNS --> JamsLambda: Notification sent
deactivate SNS
deactivate JamsLambda

SQS -> IrregularitiesLambda: Trigger with irregularities data
activate IrregularitiesLambda
IrregularitiesLambda -> IrregularitiesLambda: Transform to relational schema
IrregularitiesLambda -> Database: Insert irregularities data
activate Database
Database --> IrregularitiesLambda: Insert confirmation
deactivate Database
IrregularitiesLambda -> SNS: Publish processing status
activate SNS
SNS --> IrregularitiesLambda: Notification sent
deactivate SNS
deactivate IrregularitiesLambda

note over SQS: Retry mechanism with\nredrive policy for\nfailed messages

== API Access Flow ==
Client -> APIGateway: HTTP request (GET)
activate APIGateway
APIGateway -> APIGateway: Authentication & rate limiting
APIGateway -> APILambda: Route request
activate APILambda
APILambda -> APILambda: Validate request parameters
APILambda -> Database: Query processed data\n(jams/alerts/irregularities)
activate Database
Database --> APILambda: Return query results
deactivate Database
APILambda -> APILambda: Apply filtering & pagination
APILambda --> APIGateway: Return formatted response
deactivate APILambda
APIGateway --> Client: HTTP response (JSON)
deactivate APIGateway
deactivate S3
deactivate SQS

@enduml
